{"tid":1981942,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 我隻八哥唔識去便盤柯屎","createTime":"2020-04-21T02:55:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T16:07:56.000Z","uid":150446,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"889b66fc20a5d62afdeaf378e2d799c6b02a04e1","tid":1981942,"uid":150446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:55:20.000Z","msg":"品種：八哥犬<br />\n性別：女<br />\n年齡：一歲半<br />\n<br />\n利申：佢係識柯尿係便盤倒，柯屎都係起果個範圍 好小周圍柯，但我想佢教柯係便盤倒，咁就唔使成日拖地<br />\n<br />\n是咁的， 我好多方法都試過 <br />\n<br />\n方法1:例如佢柯屎係地下 時， 我就拎報紙包住放係便盤倒 ， 諗住佢下次柯，聞倒就會係便盤柯啦 ， 點知拎份連屎帶報紙黎咬😣 ❌❌<br />\n<br />\n方法2: 我見佢柯屎既時候就拎塊便盤俾佢 諗住叫佢柯係果到 ， 但佢就會發脾氣❌❌😣<br />\n所以都唔知點搞好， 大家有冇咩方法可以俾小弟🙏"},{"pid":"91569484a1f43aa85d03a7600eff01215066a12f","tid":1981942,"uid":273157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T03:01:24.000Z","msg":"試下養貓"},{"pid":"da3283adfb60a4f01e5ca55ad8af93d6e8802a73","tid":1981942,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T03:07:42.000Z","msg":"放多個盤囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6b8e01bc9fb9c2078101ba2de776882143f552","tid":1981942,"uid":148332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T03:12:17.000Z","msg":"見佢就痾就捉佢上盆度,然後痾完先比佢落黎,再比零食獎勵佢"},{"pid":"73c62642fc96995a012e19cd871d8cf366c8aad7","tid":1981942,"uid":63210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T01:50:57.000Z","msg":"試下比創造一個100%痾岩既地方比佢 痾中左就好誇張開心地讚佢 然後慢慢縮細痾岩範圍"},{"pid":"0437cf45ae04e460a0217abe1ff6c3f39efbadc4","tid":1981942,"uid":112901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T16:05:51.000Z","msg":"你喺佢面前用便盤屙一次先"},{"pid":"3c8a7af71c46a2382f02740fe494a6f31a29f398","tid":1981942,"uid":353981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0437cf45ae04e460a0217abe1ff6c3f39efbadc4","tid":1981942,"uid":112901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T16:05:51.000Z","msg":"你喺佢面前用便盤屙一次先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T1